#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.117"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.117:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.117:0.2"
msgid "12. Paccorohaṇivagga"
msgstr "12. The Ceremony of Descent"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.117:0.3"
msgid "117. Saṅgāravasutta"
msgstr "117. With Saṅgārava"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.117:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho saṅgāravo brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then Saṅgārava the brahmin went up to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings "
"with him."

msgctxt "an10.117:1.2"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho saṅgāravo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side and said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "an10.117:1.3"
msgid "“kiṃ nu kho, bho gotama, orimaṃ tīraṃ, kiṃ pārimaṃ tīran”ti?"
msgstr "“Master Gotama, what is the near shore? And what is the far shore?”"

msgctxt "an10.117:1.4"
msgid "“Micchādiṭṭhi kho, brāhmaṇa, orimaṃ tīraṃ, sammādiṭṭhi pārimaṃ tīraṃ;"
msgstr ""
"“Wrong view is the near shore, brahmin, and right view is the far shore."

msgctxt "an10.117:1.5"
msgid "micchāsaṅkappo orimaṃ tīraṃ, sammāsaṅkappo pārimaṃ tīraṃ;"
msgstr "Wrong thought is the near shore, and right thought is the far shore."

msgctxt "an10.117:1.6"
msgid "micchāvācā orimaṃ tīraṃ, sammāvācā pārimaṃ tīraṃ;"
msgstr "Wrong speech is the near shore, and right speech is the far shore."

msgctxt "an10.117:1.7"
msgid "micchākammanto orimaṃ tīraṃ, sammākammanto pārimaṃ tīraṃ;"
msgstr "Wrong action is the near shore, and right action is the far shore."

msgctxt "an10.117:1.8"
msgid "micchāājīvo orimaṃ tīraṃ, sammāājīvo pārimaṃ tīraṃ;"
msgstr ""
"Wrong livelihood is the near shore, and right livelihood is the far shore."

msgctxt "an10.117:1.9"
msgid "micchāvāyāmo orimaṃ tīraṃ, sammāvāyāmo pārimaṃ tīraṃ;"
msgstr "Wrong effort is the near shore, and right effort is the far shore."

msgctxt "an10.117:1.10"
msgid "micchāsati orimaṃ tīraṃ, sammāsati pārimaṃ tīraṃ;"
msgstr ""
"Wrong mindfulness is the near shore, and right mindfulness is the far shore."

msgctxt "an10.117:1.11"
msgid "micchāsamādhi orimaṃ tīraṃ, sammāsamādhi pārimaṃ tīraṃ;"
msgstr ""
"Wrong immersion is the near shore, and right immersion is the far shore."

msgctxt "an10.117:1.12"
msgid "micchāñāṇaṃ orimaṃ tīraṃ, sammāñāṇaṃ pārimaṃ tīraṃ;"
msgstr ""
"Wrong knowledge is the near shore, and right knowledge is the far shore."

msgctxt "an10.117:1.13"
msgid "micchāvimutti orimaṃ tīraṃ, sammāvimutti pārimaṃ tīranti."
msgstr "Wrong freedom is the near shore, and right freedom is the far shore."

msgctxt "an10.117:1.14"
msgid "Idaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, orimaṃ tīraṃ, idaṃ pārimaṃ tīranti."
msgstr "This is the near shore, and this is the far shore."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.117:2.1"
msgid "Appakā te manussesu,"
msgstr "Few are those among humans"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.117:2.2"
msgid "ye janā pāragāmino;"
msgstr "who cross to the far shore."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.117:2.3"
msgid "Athāyaṃ itarā pajā,"
msgstr "The rest just run"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.117:2.4"
msgid "tīramevānudhāvati."
msgstr "around on the near shore."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an10.117:3.1"
msgid "Ye ca kho sammadakkhāte,"
msgstr "When the teaching is well explained,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.117:3.2"
msgid "dhamme dhammānuvattino;"
msgstr "those who practice accordingly"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.117:3.3"
msgid "Te janā pāramessanti,"
msgstr "are the ones who will cross over"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.117:3.4"
msgid "maccudheyyaṃ suduttaraṃ."
msgstr "Death’s domain so hard to pass."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an10.117:4.1"
msgid "Kaṇhaṃ dhammaṃ vippahāya,"
msgstr "Rid of dark qualities,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.117:4.2"
msgid "Sukkaṃ bhāvetha paṇḍito;"
msgstr "an astute person should develop the bright."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.117:4.3"
msgid "Okā anokamāgamma,"
msgstr "Leaving home behind"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.117:4.4"
msgid "Viveke yattha dūramaṃ."
msgstr "for the seclusion so hard to enjoy,"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an10.117:5.1"
msgid "Tatrābhiratimiccheyya,"
msgstr "you should try to find delight there,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.117:5.2"
msgid "hitvā kāme akiñcano;"
msgstr "having left behind sensual pleasures."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.117:5.3"
msgid "Pariyodapeyya attānaṃ,"
msgstr "With no possessions, an astute person"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.117:5.4"
msgid "cittaklesehi paṇḍito."
msgstr "should cleanse themselves of mental corruptions."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.233"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an10.117:6.1"
msgid "Yesaṃ sambodhiyaṅgesu,"
msgstr "And those whose minds are rightly developed"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.117:6.2"
msgid "sammā cittaṃ subhāvitaṃ;"
msgstr "in the awakening factors;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.117:6.3"
msgid "Ādānapaṭinissagge,"
msgstr "letting go of attachments,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.117:6.4"
msgid "anupādāya ye ratā;"
msgstr "they delight in not grasping."

#. <br>
#. VAR: jutimanto → jutīmanto (bj)
msgctxt "an10.117:6.5"
msgid "Khīṇāsavā jutimanto,"
msgstr "With defilements ended, brilliant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.117:6.6"
msgid "te loke parinibbutā”ti."
msgstr "they are extinguished in this world.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.117:6.7"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
